Issues

1. Footer Links - Missing Visible Hover Underline

- Problem: Footer ArrowLinks don't show clear underline animation on hover
- Root Cause: Custom className in ArrowLink overrides UnderlineLink's animated-underline effect
- Location: src/components/layout/Footer.tsx lines 100-106, 121-127, 142-148

2. Hover Color Contrast Issues

- Problem: Some links/buttons have poor visibility on hover (text-white on light backgrounds)
- Locations:
  - Footer changelog version link (line 258, 268) - text-gray-500 hover:text-white may conflict with certain themes
  - Navigation items need better contrast feedback
  - Button hover states on gradient backgrounds

3. Max Width Consistency

- Problem: .layout class provides max-w-7xl but:
  - Not all pages use it consistently
  - Some sections stretch full-width when they shouldn't
  - Container component exists but isn't used optimally
- Current: .layout = max-w-7xl mx-auto w-11/12
- Issue: Some pages need narrower content width (e.g., legal pages, blog posts)

4. Additional UX Improvements

- Footer link hover animation visibility
- Consistent spacing patterns across pages
- Better visual feedback for interactive elements
- Mobile hover states (touch feedback)
- Focus states for keyboard navigation

Implementation Plan

Phase 1: Footer Enhancement

1. Add visible underline effect to footer links on hover
2. Improve hover states with better color transitions
3. Add smooth transform animations (translateX/Y)
4. Fix changelog version link hover contrast

Phase 2: Max Width & Layout System

1. Audit all page layouts for proper max-width usage
2. Create layout variants (narrow, default, wide, full)
3. Update pages to use Container component consistently
4. Add page-specific max-width constraints

Phase 3: Hover States & Interactive Feedback

1. Standardize button hover states across all variants
2. Improve link hover visibility (color + underline)
3. Add subtle scale/shadow effects for cards
4. Enhance focus states for accessibility

Phase 4: Responsive & Polish

1. Mobile touch feedback improvements
2. Consistent spacing system (use Tailwind spacing scale)
3. Animation performance optimization
4. Dark mode hover state refinement

Files to Modify

1. src/components/layout/Footer.tsx - Footer link hover states
2. src/styles/globals.css - Layout utilities and hover animations
3. src/components/links/ArrowLink.tsx - Better hover integration
4. src/components/links/UnderlineLink.tsx - Enhanced underline effect
5. src/components/ui/Container.tsx - Add layout variants
6. Page files - Consistent Container/layout usage

Expected Outcomes

✅ Clear visual feedback on all interactive elements
✅ Consistent max-width across all page types
✅ Better accessibility (keyboard navigation, focus states)
✅ Improved mobile experience
✅ Polished, professional UI feel
